timeline.bodyHTML:
Since only "switchTimeFormat" is acted upon here, check both the group and key.

Suggested change
if (!event.getGroup().equals("reportButton"))
{
return;
}
updateTimeFormat();
if (event.getGroup().equals("reportButton") && event.getKey().equals("switchTimeFormat"))
{
updateTimeFormat();
}
